{"tid":1402142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推比前線］重申一次，唔明點解要 hit & run 嘅請入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:51:08.000Z","uid":203845,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"614dfa5cf79d6a6aff3853431a4fd0d594e9cc3d","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 遊擊可以解決我地前線人數同裝備效果不足嘅問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n無可否認，犬隻係受過訓練，有周詳部署去圍堵示威者。<br />\n佢地有組織，有指揮，再喺人數佔優下根本冇得正面打<br />\n<br />\n既然我地人數少，咁樣就只有打遊擊<br />\n遊擊勝在可以喺人數少之下依然能夠擾亂敵軍，降低對方士氣，長遠降低對方作戰能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 遊擊可以減低我方消耗（被清場）嘅問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成場運動聽得最多嘅係：<span style=\"color: gold;\">多你一個就好多</span><br />\n對於前線就更加<br />\n多一個人被捕，除咗損失一個人之外，更加係成個士氣嘅下跌。<br />\n前線唔係condom, 但係前線都要記得呢句說話。<br />\n嚟緊嘅仗仲有排打，唔需要勉強留守<br />\n有人話：<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">不撤不散</span> 所以唔走<br />\n大佬，不散係解<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢場運動不散</span></span><br />\n而唔係唔離開遊行現場<br />\n唔打遊擊，下下少幾十人，唔使一個月，前線都己經冇晒人，場運動都玩完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 要對付狗隻，就係要逼到佢地痴線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地武力唔夠強，物理攻擊做唔到咩效果<br />\n就用精神攻擊，搞到犬隻痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據朋友引述犬隻朋友消息，犬隻而家如果要放假，都要喺狗屋standby, 唔可以離開狗屋。<br />\n<br />\n試諗下，你放大假，但係都唔可以離開公司，出到街同社交媒體就比人鬧，食嘢仲要擔心飲到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">凍撚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 你就知佢地有幾大壓力<br />\n<br />\n點樣令佢地進一步癲？就係不被捕，令佢地連發洩都冇得發洩<br />\n佢地著晒裝，然後已經冇晒人<br />\n當佢地重覆都係咁，佢地就會懷疑人生<br />\n最後成堆狗就會崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講返場運動，仲有兩樣注意地方：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.前線唔係大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請各位前線手足聽下大家意見。<br />\n知你地做得嘢，但係都要顧自己安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好做冇腦勇武<br />\n做個識撚狗嘅勇者就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而各位冷氣軍師，比意見唔係錯。<br />\n決定當然係前線決定，但係提供實時資訊係鍵戰嘅責任。<br />\n請記住：<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢場運動，要唔同崗位嘅人互相配合先會成功</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.請留力8月5嘅罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔比你地衝，但係衝都要有目的。<br />\n其實衝咗咁多次，政府會回應就回應咗啦，重覆係咁衝係冇意思<br />\n最後大家嘅升級係罷工，所以逼政府回應呢項任務就交比和理優<br />\n罷工其中一個目的，就係比前線手足休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白有手足會覺得唔衝就好似冇成果<br />\n放心啦，過咗8月5，如果政府都係唔回應<br />\n我地就要終極升級，到時先衝都未遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家真係要留力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尤其係聽日，唔好再好似今日旺角咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝每一個參與呢場運動嘅人，歷史書會記錄低我地嘅抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"717bef27b90912eae21d1ab57ef0f8e98da87f71","tid":1402142,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c82201d1eee317a8636b2dd3b9d6a3c4a596635","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"推比咁多位手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6beb560029114de99ad32d5aac7f5bfae6d863cb","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c9ed6f21b091da4aa7bb007c847f50ffe2ec863","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6525a0eae9ac5f3df9ca49cced779ee8a60ff826","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"如果認同嘅，麻煩幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4739b961d74b652acc8741ea3db00ead4532b34","tid":1402142,"uid":2730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"8月5日要見到今晚既你地啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4da305ad79f70b12ec61cee736496948a3d36e9","tid":1402142,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"887a68ffe7b807361c77f96c19c2bb2458f639f4","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4739b961d74b652acc8741ea3db00ead4532b34","tid":1402142,"uid":2730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"8月5日要見到今晚既你地啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n8月5號7區集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0f62f76419c25d8dbb061f446c6c18841f0158","tid":1402142,"uid":203845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:51:08.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家晒少少時間睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}